    "Transportation": {
      "Type": "Tour",
      "Icon": "🍷",
      "Description": "Today we actually slept in a bit and then headed on a tour for Pisa. Wow, this place is beautiful and full of history. The Tower, Cathedral, and Baptistry are all sinking in the loss soil and sand. Funny story, the local university has majors in every science, except... Architecture. Well, I think we can see why. LOL! And then the best dinner of our trip so far. Beef Stew to die for. "
